data.description: Be the first to live in this beautiful redone home! Complete Renovated 2 Family Home on 3 floors in Washington Heights. Everything is NEW! Custom designed by Architect Alexander Kahn. Live in one unit and rent out the other unit or be an investor and rent both! Great for Investors too- Rents up to $3500/month for both units. 1st Unit Duplex 3 BR/2 BA. 2nd Unit 1 BR/1 BA. Open floor plan, Eat-in kitchen with custom wood cabinets, quartz counter, marble tile, ss appliances, washer/dryer, beautiful floors, luxury bathroom fittings and Italian ceramic tile, skim coat walls, new electric and plumbing, large private back yard + large deck, full basement. Super low taxes $2810. Newburgh has waterfront restaurants with awesome Hudson River Views. Several brewery''s and winery''s are near by. Cross over the bridge and visit Beacon or jump on Metro North Train to NYC.
